#: templates/index.html:80
msgid "1. Create a Project"
msgstr "1. Create a Project"

#: templates/index.html:81
msgid ""
"Enter a Wikidata Q-ID and Commons category. The system scans all images, "
"detects faces with bounding boxes, and bootstraps from existing P180 "
"depicts claims."
msgstr ""
"Enter a Wikidata Q-ID and Commons category. The system scans all images, "
"detects faces with bounding boxes, and bootstraps from existing P180 "
"depicts claims."

#: templates/index.html:84
msgid "2. Classify Faces"
msgstr "2. Classify Faces"

#: templates/index.html:85
msgid ""
"Review detected faces one by one with Yes/No buttons. After enough "
"examples, the model classifies remaining faces automatically using face "
"encodings."
msgstr ""
"Review detected faces one by one with Yes/No buttons. After enough "
"examples, the model classifies remaining faces automatically using face "
"encodings."

#: templates/index.html:88
msgid "3. Review & Edit"
msgstr "3. Review & Edit"

#: templates/index.html:89
msgid ""
"Check model classifications. Approve matches, reject false positives, "
"redraw bounding boxes, or manually add missed faces. Each face is "
"compared independently."
msgstr ""
"Check model classifications. Approve matches, reject false positives, "
"redraw bounding boxes, or manually add missed faces. Each face is "
"compared independently."

#: templates/index.html:92
msgid "4. Send to Commons"
msgstr "4. Send to Commons"

#: templates/index.html:93
msgid ""
"Send approved matches to Commons as P180 depicts claims. Rejected "
"bootstrap faces queue P180 removal, fixing incorrect existing data."
msgstr ""
"Send approved matches to Commons as P180 depicts claims. Rejected "
"bootstrap faces queue P180 removal, fixing incorrect existing data."

